column.comment: The unique name for the asset.

column.comment: The descriptive title for the asset.

column.comment: JSON encoded access control.

column.comment: Used for clubs not listed in DB

column.comment: Number of splits in this distance

column.comment: Count of password resets since lastResetTime

column.comment: Event number suffix

column.comment: Is there a fee for this event on top of the meet fee?

column.comment: For members of multiple clubs, first claim = 1, second claim = 2, etc

column.name: timesrequired
column.comment: How many times do you have to meet a performance std to qualify at that level.

column.comment: Orders levels by priority

column.name: meet_name
column.comment: Temporary Name

column.comment: If low time not included any time under the high time will qualify at this standard.
